deliveryMessages: Or fastest delivery Friday, February 16. Order within 6 hrs 33 mins
features: 40,000 VPM Smart Toothbrush – Beauty, brains and power. The Vibe Series is a world class modern electric toothbrush packed with the most up to date technology. It features an ultra-powerful and industry leading motor producing 40,000 vibrations per minute, lithium-ion battery, ultra-fast wireless charging, 4 mode operation, smart vibration timers, 8 DuPont engineered brush heads, and a custom travel case; all with a sleek, ultra-slim, lightweight and IPX7 rated waterproof body.

Accepted by the American Dental Association (ADA) Council on Scientific Affairs – We put our money where your mouth is. Investing in premium oral care technologies has earned the Vibe Series the prestigious ADA seal of approval. It has shown efficacy in removing plaque and helping to prevent and reduce gingivitis. Vibe Series goes beyond just cleaning teeth – it provides complete oral care with unique modes that include one for whitening and polishing teeth and one for improving gum health.

8 DuPont Brush Heads & Travel Case Included - Every Vibe Series toothbrush comes with 8 brush heads engineered by world famous DuPont; a world leader in quality & materials science. Each brush head lasts 3 months so 8 will last for 2 years. Also included is a convenient custom hard shell travel case made of BPA-free plastic with space for two brush heads. Vibe Series can last 4 full weeks (2 min/2x a day) on a full charge so it's perfect for on the go travel with the included travel case.

Modern Tech For Complete Oral Care - The Vibe Series brings toothbrushes into modern times with its built in enhanced features. Ultra fast wireless charging (forget cheap USB charging), 4 distinct brushing modes and a smart vibrating notification timer are some of the enhanced features built in to the sleek waterproof and stunningly beautiful satin rose gold handle.
What's in the Box – 1 Satin Rose Gold Smart Toothbrush, 8 DuPont brush heads, 1 custom travel case, user manual, warranty card..

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 30, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Affordable and Effective
reviews.reviewText: I love my Aquasonic toothbrush! The different brushing functions, the extra included brush heads, the built-in timer, convenient travel case, the pretty color (which obviously isn’t necessary for a toothbrush, but IS a bonus -lol)… it’s so worth the money!Getting down to what really matters: I (and my dental hygienist) have noticed an improvement in my overall oral health since I switched to this sonic toothbrush, and that was the whole point. I also love the long-lasting battery time I get between charges. I am beyond satisfied with my purchase, and recommend this toothbrush to anyone.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 5, 2024
reviews.reviewText: Love the different settings, great quality, good price. Comes with a case and is perfect for traveling.Bought multiple for family members as gifts. Checkup with dentist yielded great results and no concerns.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 19, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars My first impressions of this device are very positive and a happy fuzzy feeling inside
reviews.reviewText: I bought this electric toothbrush a few months ago because it was on a good sale. It took me awhile to get around to even using. I wish I had replaced my old manual toothbrush on day one. This toothbrush is a modern miracle. The instructions said to charge the toothbrush (internal lithium ion battery) for at least 24 hours. However, if the duration of how long the "red light" stays lit on the handle of the device is any indication of how long it took to actually fully charge the battery then it may not take a full 24 hours to charge. Anyway, that point aside...The toothbrush worked just fine and the vibrations are so quick that they come off as feeling smooth. When this toothbrush touches the lips it can cause a tickling sensation. I was literally smiling multiple times because I wanted to laugh from the tickling sensations when it touched my lips.Any product that you buy that causes you to literally smile has to be a good thing.And now that I finally switched back to an electric toothbrush (this isn't my first) I am very happy with this product and find myself even brushing 2 to 3 times a day versus only one because of how easy it is and how it makes me feel.Now, since I've only been using this toothbrush less than a week I won't make any comments regarding durability or longevity. But rest assured, my first impressions are very positive. And I look forward to using this product for a very long time.To have received an electric toothbrush that is as light as a feather and comes with 8 total replacement toothbrush heads is very nice. I am very pleased with this purchase and would highly recommend it to anyone looking for a quality electric toothbrush.I will update this review if my viewpoints change over time.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 9, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars A must buy electric toothbrush, but don't buy the toothpaste with it.
reviews.reviewText: The electric tooth brush works excellent. Feels great on my teeth. It has an easy on and off switch. Comes with plenty of Toothbrush heads to last you atleast 2 years. The charge on it is amazing. This is by far the best electric toothbrush with a great price. Don't buy the toothpaste with it. The toothpaste does not work good at all. Colgate total mint stripe works so much better. I gave 4 stars just because of the toothpaste. The toothbrush 🪥 itself is 5 stars forsure.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 16, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars What a great brush! Awesome value and clean feeling.
reviews.reviewText: This was a gift purchase for my wife and I took a chance based on the amazing reviews here. This electric toothbrush did not disappoint! It holds a charge for a long time, feels and looks like it's made of quality materials, and the best part of all is that my wife said her teeth have never felt so clean before. reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 30, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Works awesome but quite noisy
reviews.reviewText: It took me a day to get used to it since it’s very loud and it is a pretty strong vibration. However, it will stop spinning if you’re pushing too hard. I also like that it has a timer. I was going to buy replacement heads for the toothbrush I have now. They cost more than the toothbrush itself. This one came with five brush heads. Plus it’s rechargeable and has a travel case.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 14, 2024
reviews.reviewText: I had a toothbrush from delta dental....it was free electric. It was not working that great anymore, not charging and I searched for the best electric toothbrush, this was #1.I decided to buy it and it was amazing to use. I find myself enjoying brushing my teeth more and I realized how terrible the other toothbrush was and this one cleans so well. It has different speed levels and the color is adorable. I bought another one for my mom because she said hers other electric toothbrush stopped working. She loves this one as much as I do and appreciates the different levels as well. They also send you 8 extra head brushes, very generous! Love this product.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 11, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Longevity and Compatibility
reviews.reviewText: Excellent brush, yes. But I chose this one over my previous Sonicare and several well-rated slightly cheaper alternatives for two reasons:1. Longevity. My wife has had the same brush for 4 years, still working great. During that same time, I've been through two Sonicares that both failed due to power button problems.2. Compatibility. Sonicare brush heads (and generic compatibles) fit. When I finish the very generous 8 brush heads that came with it, I'm confident that I'll be able to get replacements.

I was skeptical about getting an electric toothbrush but finally decided to try one. This one is great, quiet, and my teeth have never felt so clean from home brushing. I like that it has four different settings, and the battery lasts a long time so far. Make sure to charge it for a day before first use.
